Subject: Backup Didn't Run
Description:
Hi Netwrix,

We found that our schedule backup log didn't run for a month.
When we tried to start the job, it can't and prompted there are currently running backup.
What_We_Know__c:
Shadows are not backed up by Audit or moved by External storage.
Audit is not removed after External Storage saves it.
Next_Steps__c:
Confirmed the issue is resolved.
---
Update the server to 5.9.4.1 and monitor if the issue if it remains.
If not update OS from 14 to 22.
